Creates a debug value annotation that associates an SSA value with a source
variable name and location. Essential for debugger variable inspection.
@End Implementation

Process called "create_mir_debug_value" that takes value_id as Integer, variable_name as Integer, source_file as Integer, source_line as Integer, source_column as Integer, scope_id as Integer returns Integer:
    Let debug_size be 56
